<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM2.4.9">
<l>pēcu maḷavaṉ ṟituvam miṉnamar. piṟarkēṭ pataṉmuṉ paṇivār viṉaikaḷ</l>
<l>nāca matucey tiṭumā taṉmaiyā latuvē namatuy viṭamnāṇ malarmēl</l>
<l>vāca maṇivaṇ ṭaṟaipaim puṟavil maṉamain toṭunain tuḻalvār matiyil</l>
<l>nīca ravarceṉ ṟaṭaiyā tavaṉuk kiṭammā malaiyā vatunīr malaiyē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>This [place] is without describable qualities. Friends,</l>
<l rend="indent">come before others hear [about it]!</l>
<l>It will definitely produce the destruction of the karma of worshippers;</l>
<l rend="indent">therefore, that alone is our place of refuge.</l>
<l>The place for him whom is not gained by low people without intellect</l>
<l rend="indent">going [there],who waver, [their] minds along with their five senses wasting away,</l>
<l>Is the great mountain, where in fresh forests beautiful winged bees hum</l>
<l rend="indent">on new blossoms, namely Nīrmalai.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
